text: First Time on Market! Great Views from this 59XX Barr Road location and just a few minutes to downtown Ferndale! Enjoy relaxing at this affordable off road setting. Easy access to, Ferndale, I-5 and Bellingham.

This 2 story home w/ attached ADU is a dream come true. It has all the modern features you could ask for. The stylish kitchen comes complete w/ glass cabinets, quartz counters, under cabinet lighting, & SS appliances. Stay cozy by the fireplace on chilly nights. W/ 4 bedrooms, there's plenty of space for everyone, plus an office for those who work from home. Your primary bedroom is a true oasis. Prepare to be wowed by the tiled shower. An exciting feature is the 1, 127 sqft ADU. Offering a fantastic opportunity for additional income. Home is located within walking distance to schools. Fully fenced & meticulously maintained landscaping. Don't forget the gas furnace & central AC, ensuring year-round comfort. Welcome to your new sanctuary!

Flexible 4BR design! Tucked away against the greenbelt, in the back of the Alpengrove community, is this sleek, modern home with soaring ceilings in the open, light-filled great room. The private 1st level BR has its own half bath and would be fantastic for work from home. Kitchen and baths feature quartz countertops and cabinets with soft-close doors and drawers. The main level also has primary suite w/luxury bath & walk-in closet, and convenient main-floor laundry. This all-electric, energy-efficient home includes mini-split heat & A/C unit, and hybrid heat pump water heater - plus insulation package w/soundproofing. 2 car garage is XL for lots of storage. Ultimate location for easy access to I-5 and all of Bellingham!

Back on the Market. Buyer Financing fell through last minute. First time on the market since 2005- fourplex and additional multi-family lot all for one price. This well-maintained fourplex is in an established neighborhood close to schools and shopping. Each unit offers 2 bedrooms and 1.75 bath with a fireplace. The units also have their own assigned carport with adjacent separate storage. The two bottom units have spacious patios and partially fenced yards. The upstairs units each have a deck. This fourplex includes an adjoining lot zoned for either a duplex or triplex with utilities to the lot.

Welcome to your forever home in this coveted Ferndale neighborhood, featuring an expansive 4-bed, 2.5-bath layout with a dedicated office. Large windows flood the living area with natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. From the hardwood and slate flooring underfoot to the soaring vaulted ceilings. Chefs kitchen, surrounded by shaker cabinets, granite counters, stainless steel appliances and a 5-burner commercial cooktop.The primary bedroom is your personal sanctuary, with its own deck and see-through fireplace that warms both your room and the soaker tub. The 3-car garage, complete with a 10 ft door. Finally, step through French doors to a covered patio and a zen-like yard, with a cozy fire pit perfect for gatherings.

Introducing a stunning 5-acre secluded retreat in Blaine! Immaculately remodeled with meticulous attention to detail, this property boasts all-new cabinetry, quartz countertops, and lavish tile. Vaulted ceilings enhance the sense of space, while the large master bedroom offers his and her sinks and a walk-in closet. Enjoy one-level living, whether you're cozying up by the wood-burning stove or entertaining guests in your newly hydro-seeded lot. Luxury abounds with fully tiled baths featuring exquisite gold and matte black hardware, stunning interior and exterior paint, a brand-new roof, and freshly finished decks. Explore the just shy 5-acre lot with roundabout parking and a sizeable shed. Come check out this luxurious hideaway in Blaine!

This is a beautiful home in a 55+ neighborhood. This 2 bed, 2 bath home with office has a large living room, dining space, and kitchen. The spacious living room features vaulted ceilings and lots of natural light. The home features A/C and a large primary suite with jetted tub. The covered deck is great for enjoying the outdoors all year round. The dedicated shop space is heated/cooled, plus attached to the 2 car garage! This is an 1, 864 sqft home with a 600 sqft garage and a 735 sqft shop. Located on the outside edge of the development its very quiet and has pastoral views with lots of great garden space.

Welcome to 1312 Bradley Meadow Ct, a true Lynden gem! Enjoy single level living with vaulted ceilings in the open concept living room that opens to a spacious kitchen with large island, SS appliance & plenty of cabinets for storage, plus high-end flooring throughout. There are 3 large bedrooms & an office on the main floor, plus huge bonus room above the garage. Primary offers a large soaker tub, shower, double vanity, walk-in closet with built-ins & blackout shades. Off the garage you will enjoy a large mudroom with utility sink, tons of storage & built-ins to keep life organize. Private back patio is partially covered which leads out to a sunny outdoor space with hot tub & garden area. Plus, long private driveway with RV/boat parking too!

Brand new 3 bedroom, 1.75 bathroom home on over 1/4 acre lot in a dead end cul-de-sac! Beautiful kitchen with quality shaker style cabinets and the stainless appliances are included. Quartz counter tops and laminate plank flooring throughout. A centrally located mini-split keeps the whole home comfortable with efficient heat and A/C. Home also has utility room and a spacious double car garage. The back yard is splendid and just about fully fenced already! Beautiful rock work and a fire pit area! Come and experience this new, gated development with amazing mountain views.

Adorable, exceptionally well-cared-for Bellingham rambler, in quiet & cozy corner above town. Entertainment decks abound, with ideal space for gardening, potted plant beauty, private reading haven, whatever's your pleasure. 3-bedroom, 2-bath rambler, affordable living, with a lot of charm. Convenient to Bellingham; moments from popular schools; near shopping & restaurants, yet embedded in a peaceful neighborhood. Squalicum High School and Northern Heights Elementary are just around the corner. Wonderful backyard for strolls; both covered deck and sunny open deck areas. One-owner home, meticulously maintained, surrounded by great walking community.

Beautifully remodeled single wide manufactured home. Brand new white kitchen cabinets and new appliances! New paint and flooring throughout are a breath of fresh air! Lovely wood wall in second room ties everything in. Brand new windows and mini splits will keep your energy costs low and will provide cooling in the summer as well as warmth in the winter! Appliances stay including dishwasher, stove and refrigerator. The deck and landscaping are ready for you to enjoy! Do not miss this lovely gem in a quiet cul-de-sac!

Fantastic opportunity for an exceptional, ready to build, fully serviced lot in the highly desired Lynden School District. Located on the East Side of Lynden amongst the most beautiful, wide-open spaces.

Enjoy staying at The Glen in this cozy home away from home. A nice covered deck greets you as you approach the Cavco trailer, perfect for sitting on year round to enjoy all kinds of weather. A shed sits on the property as well, perfect for larger or additional storage. Inside the trailer, there is plenty of room to spread out and relax with the add-a-room. Lots of places for people to sleep in this homey retreat! The Glen is zoned recreational for 120 days of use out of the year and has all the amenities you could want, including 2 pools, hot tub, tennis court, library, laundry mat, 2 clubhouses, 24 hr security, gated entry, & play areas.
Cleared level lot with water connected and a 3 bedroom septic system recently installed. Ready to build!

Endless bay views of Lummi Bay & the San Juan Islands in this newly built home. Relax on a covered deck while enjoying the outdoor fireplace. Outside, you will find plenty of space to park your RV, and Boat. Inside, you are greeted with an open concept living space, presenting ample natural light. This home boasts superb finishes, and a well-designed floor plan, including a Dining, Family, Living Room, a Kitchen, and Primary Bedroom on the main Floor. The thoughtfully designed large kitchen has SS appliances, quartz countertops and plenty of storage space. The Downstairs showcases a second primary suite with its own separate entry and two more bedrooms. Fee simple property.
nearby_schools: Lummi High School, Lummi Elementary School, Ferndale School District

text: Opportunity knocks for anyone looking for a prime South Hill, unobstructed view - no powerlines, location to build or rehab a home. Bring your creativity to this turn of the century home or start new. Either way you'll enjoy 180 degree panoramic views - you must see it to believe it! Crystal clear blue skies and endless sunsets at your fingertips on a street lined with gorgeous homes. How rare to have such a clear view of the bay, islands, mountains, and city lights with views toward Fairhaven and Bellingham Harbor! The home offers a great base for your new project including a detached garage w/ alley access. New laws may present future opportunity for multiple dwellings - attached or detached. Don't let this one pass you by!

Enjoy this warm and cozy beach house on the shores of Lummi Bay, with views of the San Juans. With 2 living spaces, including 5 bedrooms, 4 bathrooms, and 2 kitchens, there are endless opportunities. Make this your summer home, or create a rental property and an investment for your future. Sits on a large double lot with 100 feet of waterfront, and your very own boat launch! Must see to appreciate what this house has to offer. Imported tile roof, newer furnace with A/C, newer grinder pump installed, 2 entrances, large deck for year round viewing pleasure.
nearby_schools: Lummi High School, Lummi Elementary School, Ferndale School District

text: One Level Living, 3-bed, 2-bath offers a comfortable and inviting living space with vaulted ceiling. entryway complete with a closet. The floor to ceiling custom fireplace adds a touch of warmth and character to the living area, creating the perfect ambiance for cozy evenings. Spacious kitchen boasts plenty of counter space and features a walk-in pantry and an island dining area. Step out onto the covered back porch, which offers privacy and can be upgraded to include a heaterall season entertaining. The primary bedroom is a true retreat double vanity, spacious tile shower with custom glass door. room off the living is perfect for office or guest room. this house ready to become your dream home. House Plan=Prairie. Move in Ready today!

BEST PRICED HOME IN SUMAS! Check out this bright & clean and very affordable 3 bed, 1 full bath home in wonderful Sumas. This zero lot line home boasts all new paint inside and out, new carpets, all new stainless appliances, new lighting with smart/dimmable switches and all bedrooms have new modern ceiling fans. A large kitchen with huge countertop would make this a bakers dream. Large dining room area complete with a laundry/mud room. All appliances included & the home has forced air heating. Home also has a great storage area for lawnmower, bikes, freezer and more. Located on a low traveled street. Less than 1 block away from the Library! This home is move in ready and would make a great first time home. Stop renting & build some equity!

Gorgeous peaceful and tranquil beachfront with beach rights property on Lummi Island. Borders a nature reserve and is very private. Lots of options for building. Beautiful Madrona trees on property. Nature abound with birds, sea life, view of Mt Baker and Bellingham Bay. Private beach for kayaking and crabbing. Lummi Scenic Estates offers a member owned marina and clubhouse, swim lake and playground. Marina has a boat launch, dock and boat trailer storage. Build your dream while living in the off grid tiny house.
nearby_schools: Lummi High School, Lummi Elementary School, Ferndale School District

text: Home and condominium buyers, this is a recently remodeled South Hill, 3-bedroom, 1.75 bath, bay view home, which comes with a low maintenance yard and is located near the heart of Fairhaven. The home was remodeled by Moceri Construction in 2018, with additional improvements by Ethos West. As the yard requires little maintenance, it is a perfect alternative option to a condominium. Included is off street and covered parking--a rare find indeed. Walk from home to all your favorite activities; restaurants, coffee shops and bakeries, as all are close by.

Bellingham Bay View Home w/ remodeled Main floor, updated bsmt. Upper Kitchen is High-end. Lower Kitchen is original. ADU/rental poss downstairs. Lot runs to Morey Ave- new regs may allow added rental units. Once inside, youll be drawn to the full width Bay view. On the large deck you have an ever-changing seascape. Coming back inside, notice all the varnished natural woodwork & solid wood floors. The custom Kitchen is a cooks delight w/ Viking Range & SS appliances. Down the hall is a bath w lg tile shower, Bedroom, & Main Suite w/ walk-in closet, tub/toilet/tiled-shower/& double sinks. Downstairs: Family Room, Office/Br, ba, laundry, & Kitchen-Dining Room. Extra bsmt sq ft (shop) to convert to large 2nd Ensuite bed/bath.

This is it, city living with a country feel! You'll find yourself just minutes away from schools, parks, groceries, dining, and all the other necessary conveniences! The property is NOT in a flood zone, and the City of Nooksack makes permitting a breeze. Come bring your plans and start building your dream today!

Welcome to condo living on the Raspberry Ridge GC. This lovely condo looks out toward the 5th hole and offers views of the course and mountains. Single level home that feels less like a condo with a large 2 car garage & private driveway. Step inside to an open & spacious main living space blending with the kitchen and dining. Brand new laminate flooring adds a contemporary touch & easy to maintain. Two bedrooms including a primary suite with walk in closet & private bathroom. Small flex area off laundry room. The back patio offers a gas hookup for your barbecue. Raspberry Ridge is a sought after 55+ community with easy access to Bellingham and Lynden while offering access to a quick round of golf or enjoying the game from your patio.

Modern, cozy, rustic A-Frame on a dead end street, ample space for outdoor living on this large corner lot. House has been fully updated with brand new septic tank, new metal roof, fully updated electrical including 50 amp RV hook up/EV charger. Interior features LVP flooring throughout, new kitchen with butcher block counters and all new appliances. Cozy bathroom with tiled corner shower and lower spout perfect for washing feet or furry friends. Never worry about running out of hot water with the new tankless water heater. $20, 000 of previously approved plans for an attached garage and second story addition to convey with house. Footings already inspected and poured. Come make this beautiful house home.

Meticulously maintained home nestled on a serene tiered lot backing onto a tranquil pond and greenspace. The spacious floor plan boasts a large kitchen, living room & great room, perfect for unforgettable gatherings. Featuring 9-foot ceilings, a luxurious primary bedroom with ensuite bath & walk-in closet, shaker-style maple cabinets, granite-tile counters, hardwood oak floors, large kitchen island & laundry room with additional utility sink and ample storage. Recent upgrades include a new roof (2021) and a new furnace and central A/C (2022). The sunlit SW-facing deck & generously sized yard are ideal for both relaxation and lively entertainment. Conveniently located near charming downtown Ferndale and walking distance to multiple schools.

Birch Bay Village prime building lot. Rare no issues level, large, ideally located site. 25% larger than average-sized lot in the community at 12, 000 + sq. ft. Only a block from entry gate & 1 of the few remaining undeveloped lots on Comox Ridge. Ideal for custom or spec home. Peace of mind 24/7 manned guard gated security. Birch Bay Village residents enjoy access to newly completed private marina, tennis, pickleball, clubhouse, pool, beach access, golf & more. Located in the Pacific NW's famous Rain Shadow with only 27 avg. rainfall per year. 15 minutes to U.S./ Canada Border and under 30 minutes to Bellingham. Come Home to a Vacation, Come Home to Birch Bay Village . Build your dream home today or hold as a prudent investment.

This charming, fully remodeled 2-bedroom, 1-bath condo is a true gem. No stairs! Step inside to discover a beautifully updated interior, featuring a cozy living space and a tastefully designed kitchen with modern appliances and delightful finishes. The bright and airy bedrooms offer comfort and tranquility, while the sleek bathroom exudes style and functionality. Nestled in a desirable location, this home provides easy access to local amenities, parks, and schools. Includes two assigned parking spots. A cozy back patio with a custom cover keeps you dry in any weather. Don't miss out on the cutest kitchen in townschedule your viewing today!

Beautifully updated 2 bedroom condo in the Raspberry Ridge 55+ Community. This single level, duplex style condo features a spacious single level layout. The tastefully updated kitchen is complete with Kitchen Aid appliances, large pantry, and island with prep sink. Primary bedroom with bath and walk-in closet. Many upgrades throughout, including wood floors, Hunter Douglas blinds, ceiling fans and central A/C. Beautiful, low maintenance outdoor space with private patio overlooking Raspberry Ridge Golf Course. Attached garage includes utility sink, large workbench, and storage space. Centrally located between Bellingham and Lynden allows for easy access to shopping and services.

Live the good life in this gorgeous no stairs rambler in the Horizon Community in Blaine, WA. This open concept 3 bed, 3 bath home with WATER VIEWS features a chef's kitchen with quartz counters, double ovens, stainless appliances & walk in butlers pantry with wine fridge. Enjoy sunsets over the Bay or bird watching from the expansive covered deck. Retreat to the primary suite with a spa-like bathroom offering heated tile floors, a soaker tub, double vanity, custom tiled shower & completed with 2 walk-in closets! Cozy modern fireplace to warm up & AC to cool down. Nestled in a picturesque setting with views of the Cascade Mts, Birch Bay, and the Salish Sea, enjoy miles of walking trails in the community and an easy stroll to Birch Bay.

Brand new townhome in Bellingham's Sunset Village community. This 3 story, 3 bedroom, 1.75 bath end unit features an oversized garage, stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops & mixed cabinetry. Walkable to shopping, dining, bus line, & trail system. Don't miss out on a great opportunity!

Welcome to your ultimate summer escape at Latitude 49 Resort in Birch Bay! Step into this darling home where a spacious covered deck sets the stage for relaxation. Store your beach gear and essentials in the convenient storage shed. But the real magic lies in the resort amenities waiting just beyond your doorstep. Dive into vacation mode with access to the outdoor pool, hot tub, pickleball courts, and more. Afterward, gather with friends and neighbors in the clubhouse for some quality time in the recreational area. With meticulous grounds and secured entry, you can enjoy peace of mind. Plus, with low monthly HOA dues and all furnishings and appliances included. Don't let this opportunity slip away experience 180 days of vacation paradise!

Welcome to Northview, where contemporary solar living meets stunning mountain and golf course views. Elevate your lifestyle with this better than new, model home proudly featured in Bellingham Alive. Open concept layout blends functionality and elegance. Modern kitchen boasts high end finishes, an over-sized island and a walk-in pantry with additional flex space. Mini-split heat pump ensures comfort, while solar panels maximize savings, epitomizing eco-friendly living. Wired for electric car charging. Large, fully fenced yard offers private retreat overlooking the golf course. Enjoy nearby amenities like brand new regional Cordata park, scenic bike lanes, trails, & shopping. Easy access to I-5 puts Seattle & Vancouver city life within reach.

Welcome to the Gardiner Terrace Community! This 3 bed, 2 full bath single level home has flowing open floor plan. Kitchen has been fully updated and has newer stainless steel appliances. Formal dining room, eating space off kitchen, breakfast bar and family room make this home perfect for entertaining. Primary bedroom has en suite bath with soaking tub, shower and spacious walk-in closet. Radiant heat throughout with new high-end/tech boiler. Utility room with nice washer/dryer set leads to huge 3 car garage with workspace for all of your projects and toys! Located on a fully fenced, well-kept, 12, 197 sqft lot. Close to schools, parks, shopping, amenities, restaurants and less than 20 minutes to Bellingham!

This condo is a prime location walkable to WWU, downtown Bellingham, Co-op and farmers market. Easy access to trails, waterfront parks, & Fairhaven.Covered assigned parking space, on-site laundry facilities, & secure 6x6 storage on-site.The living room double bed unit with built-in desk, & shelving stays.The condo has an updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances, butcher block counters, & renovated bathroom.Radiant heat & closet organizers enhance the convenience and practicality of this condo.There are breathtaking views of the water, cityscape, & sunsets from the large covered balcony.Ramp access from High Street adds to the accessibility and convenience of entering the unit, making it ideal for individuals with mobility considerations.

Check out this nearly new, modern home in the Mt Baker Rim community. Whether a full time residence or vacation home, this almost 1, 600 sqft home features a gorgeous kitchen with stainless appliances and quartz counters, perfect for entertaining large groups. Situated on a very nice flat and sunny lot with all the modern features you might need including a metal roof, generator, gorgeous firepit area, A/C and much more! Trimmed out with cedar accents on the outside, planked vaulted ceilings inside and a bright open floorplan, this home lives large with a bedroom, gear room, and office/den on the main floor and a loft sitting area along with another large bedroom on the second floor. With 2 bathrooms including laundry, this home has it all!

Mid-county gem in Lynden Schools! 2 homes + shop on 2.85 acres boast stunning views of Mt. Baker and Twin Sisters. Set back off the road in private park-like setting, the main house, 2500 sq ft, features mid-century charm with a daylight basement and split-level formal living and dining with vaulted ceilings, open beams, rock wall, gas FP, and huge picture windows that take in the view. 4 bd, 2.5 ba, formal and informal space, primary bd with 3/4 bath, family room w/ gas FP and attached XL 2-car garage/workroom. Second home, 1030 sq ft, single-story with 3 bd, 2 ba, offers privacy with a separate drive. A 36'x60' insulated/heated shop with crane and offices complete the package. Mature cedars, fenced yards, circular driveways and more!

Here is a wonderful opportunity to develop this property in the Puget neighborhood into building lots. The City of Bellingham advised that the 15 lots need to have 2 combined into 1 and have new lot line adjustments. Water is run down the road, electricity, and gas are to the corner. Still needs a road, sewer, and storm drain. Buyers are to check with COB to verify all information.

The perfect single-story home in Lynden, just like new! A 2022 build with vaulted ceilings and a bright, welcoming great room. Stainless steel appliances, beautiful matching granite countertops throughout, modern hardware and finishes, gas stove, 3 beds | 2 bathrooms, a nice-sized laundry room and private, fenced yard for your furry friends. This move-in ready home is waiting for you! Come live the Lynden dream in this established neighborhood.
